## 概念代码

```c++
class IFlyweight 
{
	virtual void operayion()
};

class CFlyweight : public IFlyweight
{
public:
	CFlyweight(int id):m_id(id) {}
private:
	int m_id;
};

class CFlyweightFactory
{
private:
	std::map<int, IFlyweight*> m_map;

	IFlyweight* getFlyweight(int id)
	{
		auto it = m_map.find(id);
		if (it == m_map.end())
		{
			m_map[i] = new CFlyweight(i);
		}
		return m_map[i];
	}
}
```
